visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Peralta

designer: Astigmatic

approved: true
description: <p>The Peralta typeface is an egyptian \
  slab serif gone haywire. You'll find that Capitals \
  and Lowercase have opposite weight distributions, \
  as well as an all-around offbeat nature, and yet \
  it all works to create a delightfully comic typeface.</p>

font.Peralta-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Peralta-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

